<div class="insight-board mockup-chrome">
  <div class="mockup-header">
    <div class="traffic-lights"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
    <div class="mono muted">insights.sql → actions</div>
  </div>
  <div class="insight-board-body">
    <div class="insight-row high">
      <span>01</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Onboarding asks for too much too early.</strong>
        <p>42% of paid users leave before sign up. Test guest mode.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="insight-row">
      <span>02</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Best users come from the study-session creative.</strong>
        <p>D7 retention is 18% higher than generic productivity ads.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="insight-row">
      <span>03</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Paywall is too early for ad-acquired users.</strong>
        <p>Move the trial offer after first completed project.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="insight-row">
      <span>04</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Do not raise spend yet.</strong>
        <p>CAC is promising, but activation still leaks too much.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .insight-board {
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .insight-board-body {
    padding: 16px;
    display: grid;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .insight-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 42px minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 15px;
    background: rgba(14, 14, 17, 0.48);
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
  }
  .insight-row.high {
    border-color: color-mix(in oklab, var(--accent) 38%, var(--hairline));
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      var(--accent-tint),
      rgba(14, 14, 17, 0.48)
    );
  }
  .insight-row span {
    color: var(--accent-2);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .insight-row strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }
  .insight-row p {
    color: var(--body);
    margin: 5px 0 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .insight-board {
      max-width: 760px;
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
